latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Purple A11y is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/purple-a11y-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Improvements
- Add WCAG SCs 1.4.1, 2.2.1 and 2.2.2 to percentage passes in report
- Enhanced connectivity check
- Speed up screenshots by limiting to 50 images per page scan
- Increase time allowed for each page scan up from 60 to 90 seconds
- Enhanced check to evaluate page load state
- Update Crawlee 3.8.1 and Playwright to 1.44.1

#### Bug fixes
- Support fixes for basic auth websites
